Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.47,0:00:05.48,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\pos(642,586)\fad(500,450)}﻿Galactic Calendar, Year 211
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.59,0:00:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Year 0 of the Third Galactic Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.09,0:00:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time, though, it was called Year 71 of the True Calendar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.93,0:00:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It's way out in the backwaters of the galaxy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.73,0:00:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I suppose it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.10,0:00:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the planet called "Earth"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.13,0:00:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿The Empire began from such a tiny world?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.52,0:00:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Not even from a world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It all began from a single Module.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.86,0:00:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿"Module"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.49,0:00:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose "Module" is an obsolete word now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Our originator, the Founder, lost many classmates in the battle for Module 77, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.43,0:00:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,he happened across the Magius.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.99,0:02:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Rukino Saki...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Will you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.80,0:02:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to make me spend the rest of my life to pay for what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.63,0:02:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Are you some kind of idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm an idol, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.05,0:02:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It's impossible for me to belong to one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.59,0:02:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But what I did to you was—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You're such a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an entertainer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.54,0:02:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done that tons of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I was part of an adult, filthy world that you know nothing about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.03,0:02:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not that kind of—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You know perfectly well what that was.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.36,0:02:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It was a Kamitsuki attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go rescue our prime minister, Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.37,0:03:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I don't hate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.56,0:03:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, hey! Why don't you come join us?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.07,0:03:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Rejected...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I rejected her...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sashinami Shoko. We're moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If you sit here, your father will have died for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,L-elf! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:04:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The school. Sashinami is with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My Valvrave will be offline for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, use me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Drive the Dorssian soldiers out of the Module!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an effective decision, coming from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me in front of the #2 track. I'll pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood. And tell Shoko something for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're going to win, no matter what.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.48,0:04:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell Haruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Would Tokishima Haruto suffer if he knew he killed Prime Minister Sashinami?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are so much alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.88,0:04:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Bulkhead G-17 has been breached!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.05,0:04:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Power feed to spaceport block is falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.91,0:04:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirmation of drill launch by enemy forces that infiltrated the Pit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It will arrive at the school in 60 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no... My sister is in—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a drill, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't look good...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's climbing this way! Get clear, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Something stings...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Hirata?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! It's gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, it's headed right for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.13,0:05:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It's gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Move to higher ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Bansho, run! It's not safe here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Poison gas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.19,0:05:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! If that drill reaches the surface, poison gas will spread through the whole Module!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.98,0:05:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We'll all die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's ignoring the New Guinea Treaty, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so like you, Cain, a man who puts results ahead of methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the hero who was awarded three Dorssian medals of valor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the central figure of the reformation 12 years ago, the Chancellor's right-hand man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,As well as the man who tamed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a soldier, I take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.38,0:05:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:06:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The wound in your left shoulder is from a gunshot. A .45 caliber frangible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The rough scar left from the suturing tells me that it was a battlefield patch job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging from the cleanliness of your hands, you're either a military surgeon or a scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.65,0:06:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll interrogate him separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.84,0:06:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Add him to the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.69,0:06:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The graduation ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Poison gas?! These bastards are fighting dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If we don't do something, they'll be wiped out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We have to stop that drill no matter what it takes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.67,0:06:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's head to the Pit's entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.05,0:06:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be our shield! Yamada, you're support!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.43,0:06:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Rukino, you're our lead-off man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It's "Thunder"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.02,0:06:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha... Haru—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:07:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Sashinami? It's me, Renbokoji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, save my sister! Save Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.74,0:07:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The drill is headed right for the school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If we don't do something Akira will— Please!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She had a rough time at school a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.10,0:07:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why she's scared of going outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She hasn't answered any of my texts or calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Sashinami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only person— 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want your help!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Akira-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿I'm not scared. I'm here because I love this place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There aren't any people that I hate here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.31,0:07:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Idiots are automatically weeded out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is clean and just and a world that's only mine!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let them take Unit 1?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A Trojan horse. We'll be hidden in the engine, and they'll take us right to the heart of their operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.24,0:07:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a situation where we can worry about risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Cain that we're up against!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.32,0:08:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They were supposed to be keeping an eye on Unit 1...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Cain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, my greatest masterpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, shall we begin the graduation ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thunder's gonna yank out that poison gas of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Piedra del Sol unit, the Valvraves are headed your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But A-drei has gone to join the Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Captain informed me. It's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Nope, nope!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I told you that these chumps won't work on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:09:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a taste of my Machine Gun Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd ya like that thumping?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Lame tricks like that aren't gonna work against—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Huh? My temperature's spiking!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All I did was punch the thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Hey, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dude, seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamada! Can't you move?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, I'm over 100%!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.28,0:09:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Irons? Is that their plan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The principle is simplicity itself. But Lord Cain is a great man indeed to have been able to notice it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a hot idea, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A Trojan horse, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a classic, but not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be taking this machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.64,0:09:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,For the future of the clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You killed them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Immortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought, he's third generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No hesitation to kill your former teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.08,0:10:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a proficiency rating of S. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...surely I must have ingrained it in you by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't win against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.39,0:10:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Drill has reached sublevel 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's even raising the temperature of my shield?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We're out of time! All right, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.41,0:10:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how formidable the defensive capabilities that unit boasts...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.12,0:10:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use! No use! No use!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The Piedra del Sol is even more powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Inuzuka-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still weak on defense, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Proficiency rating, E.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Impossible... How can he be beating me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Run, L-elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Wha—?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.33,0:11:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one who can turn the tide!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Run and win! In this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a sensible decision, coming from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.09,0:11:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's made a friend, has he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,In a long life, friends are a precious thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, A-drei?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The Captain called on me to act as interrogator.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Once it's all over, I'll take your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You will become my left eye, and together, we shall see my revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy forces are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.78,0:12:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you stay there, you'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So what?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the other choice is going outside, I'd rather die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like telling me to devolve into a water flea or something.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to live by lowering myself to that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're the water flea, big brother, you can go ahead and live surrounded by paramecia.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll live by myself and die by myself!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.55,0:12:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd rather die? Not a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The key is to not let them touch you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:13:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.54,0:13:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Die. I'll boil your blood in your veins.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Valvrave units have all shut down...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Isn't this bad...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.43,0:13:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Lady Takahi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Iori! Where's Tokishima?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he's with L-elf...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just "think"! Get him on the line right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Drill has reached sub-level 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm fine by myself, I'm telling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need your help! Don't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Your voice, your smile, the heat of your body, it'll all be gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.13,0:13:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never meet anyone again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be able to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.46,0:13:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be able to hate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.56,0:13:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Or be touched by anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Y-You're just like everyone else.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You laugh at me! Pity me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You get mad at me and tell me to go outside!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm mad, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}See?! I told you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.45,0:13:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't remember us ever becoming friends...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We are starting now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't decide that by yourself!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Too late, I already have!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's so self-centered...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.03,0:14:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Never underestimate a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I, we're friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Sho—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Drill has reached sub-level 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We're done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.69,0:14:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not working...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.93,0:14:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's get you nice and dean, young lady!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You filthy thing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My, what lovely hair you have!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think you'd look good in a short cut!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.12,0:15:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your scalp doesn't itch anywhere, does it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I promised her...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿That we'd—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come shopping with me at the supermarket!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿SUPERMARKET!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm out! I made it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko! Shoko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko! Shoko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Shoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.22,0:16:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Shoko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.68,0:16:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Shoko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Shoko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Already did...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko... Shoko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.16,0:17:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿She's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not stopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.51,0:18:05.27,Alt,,0,0,0,,﻿"HACKING CODE..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.77,0:18:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿My weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What the—?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm being hacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Unit 6!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's piloting it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,H-neun! Launch your Waffe squadron!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad guys get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,H-neun! What are you playing at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me! The machines did it on their own!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.52,0:19:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Shoot, Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Him? But he's not in a mecha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot him! He's too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.53,0:19:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll... I'll protect our country!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We all promised that we'd never give up, not to the bitter end!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Cain, not even you could have survived that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿He dodged it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.07,0:20:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.49,0:20:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I make it clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.45,0:20:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.71,0:20:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿That's—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.50,0:20:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I've won, Cain. That unit doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.29,0:21:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure this brings back nothing but bad memories for you, but I need you, Ploo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.34,0:21:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse those humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.22,0:21:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.80,0:21:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,B...ro—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.14,0:21:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It talked?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.68,0:21:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Bro... Bro—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.05,0:21:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.33,0:21:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's taken human form!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.38,0:21:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 2 was broken...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.38,0:21:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Only modified students can operate the Valvraves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.97,0:21:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He can use the Valvrave's light without a Valvrave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.22,0:21:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,All these phenomena suggest that he is not human!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.47,0:21:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Cain, what in the world are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.21,0:22:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We are the Magius.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.75,0:22:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who dwell in the shadows of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.44,0:23:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll die? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.24,0:23:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Select the next pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.57,0:23:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.05,0:24:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto! Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.36,0:24:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿L-elf, damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.91,0:24:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Tokishima Haruto who proposed human experimentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.66,0:24:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll end this curse with us!
